# Input

```yml
? explicit key # Empty value
? |
  block key
: - one # Explicit compact
  - two # block value

```


# Prettier differences

```diff
--- Prettier
+++ Biome
@@ -1,5 +1,5 @@
-? explicit key # Empty value
+? explicit key 
 ? |
   block key
 : - one # Explicit compact
-  - two # block value
+  - two 
```

# Output

```yml
? explicit key 
? |
  block key
: - one # Explicit compact
  - two 
```
